Citation.sAbstract: A total of 13 796 compressed liquid density measurements for  2,3,3,3-tetrafluoroprop-1-ene (R1234yf) for eight isotherms evenly spaced  from (283.15 to 353.15) K for pressures from near saturation to 35 MPa  are presented. In addition, a saturated liquid density correlation and a Tait  correlation are developed.

ePurifMethod: De-gassed by freezing and melting in vacuum
